Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I knew it, I abandoned happiness to survive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.15,0:00:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lying to myself, I danced clinging on to illusions
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the edge of my vision when I close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was searching for your smile
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With our memories fading
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We hold on to our dreams and run  Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:01:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These feelings that I shut away in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll now grasp them again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!  I thought I won, but he’s tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.53,0:01:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m physically at my limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven’t had such a heated duel in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This fight is exciting, Valon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dueling you is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:01:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only the stakes weren’t so high...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:02:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonouchi must be dueling right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he loses, he’ll lose his soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!  But the map says he’s around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to search the alleys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sensed that Jonouchi’s Claw of Hermos activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don’t sense anything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean Jonouchi lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s find Jonouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, Valon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re good too, Jonouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody has fought me this well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re #1 when it comes to toughness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re fighting hard, but neither’s spirit is breaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A duel this heated is what I was looking for!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to fight too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I activated Aura Armor, I have to pay half my life points!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set two cards and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.  I draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During my Standby Phase, I Special Summon Psychic Armor Head from my graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate a spell card from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phoenix Gravitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?  It can’t be!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This spell card Special Summons four Armor Monsters from my graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resurrect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burning Knuckle, Jet Gauntlet, Over Boost and Active Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phoenix Gravitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You played well to get this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a true duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I’ll defeat you with all my might!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you’re the one who’ll be defeated, Valon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I flip over my set card!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Graverobber!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took a card from your graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bang Blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I flip over another card!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take One Chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I draw one random card from my graveyard and activate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I chose…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please bring me power!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He drew something good again at the last moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Claw of Hermos’s effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It fuses with Big Bang Blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bang Dragon Blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to use your weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I was hoping for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A great duel that gets me excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a great duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the most fun duel ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will end it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burning Knuckle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bang Dragon Blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s been fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the best duel ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Big Bang Dragon Blow’s effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By tributing a monster, all your monsters are destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you take damage equal to their total attack points!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who you cared for, I thought I could make you fall for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may look pathetic, but I have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Valon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonouchi, take care of Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Valon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you lost, Valon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your soul will nourish our god.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re next, Mai Kujaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show the darkness in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Valon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Valon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai, you and I are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to keep winning to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:10:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I finally found a reason to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s you, Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said, “Never duel for someone else.”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Duel and win for yourself.”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why you lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Valon did his best as a duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t even let you talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn’t Valon your enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I admire a duelist who fights with all his strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai, bring it on.  Duel me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only understand how you feel by dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s do it, Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s duel with all our strength so we’re left with no regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go easy on me like last time, I’ll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonouchi, take care of Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me everything you got!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I’ll give it my all, like a duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m counting on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.47,0:11:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That light was from Jonouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the right direction, but where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, isn’t it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one’s here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be due to Doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won’t let us through.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:13:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no time to waste on you weaklings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you won’t let me through...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…I’ll make you by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!  I draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon Cyber Harpie in attack position!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m still hurt from my last duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon Blue Flame Swordsman in attack position!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.  I can’t see well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C’mon, body.  Hang in there a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Cyber Harpie and your Blue Flame Swordsman both have 1800 attack points.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not like you to end your turn without doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry.  I’m not going easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned something after fighting Valon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We communicated more by dueling than with words.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.19,0:14:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understood how he felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.42,0:14:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I’m taking you seriously too, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you’ll know how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I want to know how you really feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll never understand how I feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.84,0:14:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How it feels to hunger for victory and keep fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn’t understand you so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don’t want to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you’re thinking, I’m just going to crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!  I draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon another Cyber Harpie in attack position!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I activate a spell card from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aero Nail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By equipping Aero Nail, Cyber Harpie gains 300 attack points!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s her special Harpie Lady combo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpie attacks Blue Flame Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Blue Flame Swordsman is destroyed, its effect activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Special Summon Flame Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Swordsman and your other Harpie both have 1800 attack points.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to attack and destroy them both, Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I attack, I’ll make sure to shave your life points!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a card and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Valon’s deck focused on offense, but Mai’s deck balances offense and defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She uses spell and trap cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I’m not careful, she’ll lock me down quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.01,0:16:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll make you come to your senses, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tribute Scapegoat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Panther Warrior attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I flip over my set card!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpie Lady Sparrow Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only activate this trap card when I have at least two Harpie Ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The flaming wings block and negate all attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we continued, I may have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…Without telling Mai anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I’ll...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tribute Flame Swordsman to summon Cyber-Tech Alligator in attack position!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.43,0:17:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cyber-Tech Alligator!  Attack Cyber Harpie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally play a real duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aero Nail’s effect activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it goes to the graveyard, I can equip it on a Harpie Lady on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a card and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!  I draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.  The Seal of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Seal of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonouchi is over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there’s a Seal...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t escape anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re the only ones here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can fight until one of us falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.  I won’t run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.90,0:19:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Seal brings out the darkness in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Yugi couldn’t overcome its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with this duel, I want to erase the darkness in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon Cyber Harpie in attack position!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:20:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to The Seal of Orichalcos’s effect, Harpies gain 500 attack points!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpie, attack Cyber-Tech Alligator!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then attack Jonouchi directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I flip over my set card!  Scapegoat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I expected that move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I flip over my set card!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nightmare Tri-Mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For every non-Normal Summoned monster you have, this trap card Special Summon a Copy Token.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpie Lady!  Attack Scapegoat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The copied Harpies can’t attack this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for the same trick as last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic, Jonouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.89,0:21:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.62,0:21:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve actually improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t fall for your bluffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.44,0:21:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll win this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t run.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai, I’ll bring you back this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.07,0:22:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The streets flow by, colored in red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.48,0:22:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you notice your pain, it changes to joy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.05,0:22:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People learn of friendship every time they wipe their tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.09,0:22:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the warm strength you gave me, I’ll change them into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing emotions don’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.81,0:22:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll live feeling them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me to be me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.69,0:22:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Overflowing friendship heals me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.86,0:23:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our chance meeting was real
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll both understand that someday
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.32,0:23:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonouchi defeated Valon in a fierce fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with no time to rest, he begins dueling Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonouchi wants to know how Mai feels, and let her know how he feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he’s damaged from his duel with Valon, ready to collapse at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.06,0:23:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Jonouchi’s emotions reach Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.35,0:23:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh!:\NBitter Victory
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.45,0:23:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel, standby!
